        public static final UnitOfUsages Allowed_usage_start_page
        Page number where allowed usage begins. <Quantity> should contain an absolute page number, counting the cover as page 1. (This type of page numbering should not be used where the e-publication has no fixed pagination). Use with (max number of) Pages, Percentage of content, or End page to specify pages allowed in Preview <p>NOTE: Introduced in Onix3

(This type of page numbering should not be used where the e-publication has no fixed pagination). Use with Start page to specify pages allowed in a preview <p>NOTE: Introduced in Onix3
